OL,6,FAn unlicensed taxi driver has been
OL,7,Fjailed after he falsely imprisoned and
OL,8,Fsexually assaulted a woman in his car.
OL,10,FWilliam King, 44, has also been given
OL,11,Fa Sexual Offences Prevention Order to
OL,12,Frestrict his behaviour.
OL,14,FKing picked up the woman and her male
OL,15,Ffriend from St Peter Port in Guernsey
OL,16,Fin the early hours of Sunday 9 April
OL,17,F2023, pretending he would take them
OL,18,Fboth home.
