OL,6,FHe dropped off the friend first before
OL,7,Fdriving her around until she fell
OL,8,Fasleep - the woman then woke up to
OL,9,Ffind King sexually assaulting her.
OL,11,FDeputy Chief Officer Richard Bell from
OL,12,FGuernsey Police says investigators
OL,13,Fconcluded that King had been driving
OL,14,Faround the island from 00:30am until
OL,15,F03:30am "looking for intoxicated women
OL,16,Fto target".
