OL,6,FThe Royal Court found King was unfit
OL,7,Fto stand trial but heard the evidence
OL,8,Fand ruled he had "done the physical
OL,9,Facts that make up the offences" of
OL,10,Fsexual assault and false imprisonment.
OL,12,FDeputy Chief Officer Bell adds: "We
OL,13,Fhave taken the decision to name him
OL,14,Ftoday with the support of the victim,
OL,15,Fto reassure the community that even in
OL,16,Fthese unusual circumstances the police
OL,17,Fand law officers will rigorously
OL,18,Fpursue measures to protect the public
OL,19,Fand have done so in this case.
