OL,6,F"We would like to take this
OL,7,Fopportunity to commend the bravery,
OL,8,Fresilience, and commitment of the
OL,9,Fvictim in helping us to pursue this
OL,10,Fdifficult and important case as it
OL,11,Fwent through multiple court hearings.
OL,13,F"Guernsey Police would like to remind
OL,14,Fthe community of the dangers of using
OL,15,Funlicensed or 'Facebook' taxis.
OL,17,F"Please plan ahead if you are heading
OL,18,Fout for the evening, especially if
OL,19,Fconsuming alcohol.
